16 and governmental entities authorized by existing law to have access to such
17 confidential information. (NRS 703.190, 703.196)
18 This bill provides that if any such confidential information is also privileged,
19 the privilege is not waived as a result of the confidential information being
20 disclosed or made available to the Commission, its officers and employees, and
21 other persons and governmental entities authorized by existing law to have access
22 to the confidential information.
